value: I will carry out my duty!
So, this is the garb of the Order of Heroes. Fits me well enough. What say you?
Fear not. Despite the new look, I am still the same Eliwood you've come to know.
The Kingdom of Askr has a rich culture. There is much to learn here.
Prince Alfonse and I have a good deal in common. He cares for his people as much as I do mine.
It feels a little frivolous to fuss over appearances, but...I do look good, don't I?
You…you haven't heard Hector say anything about this outfit yet, have you? *pause* So there's still hope he hasn't noticed…
I appreciate all the time we've had to bond. I hope we can continue to fight together, side by side.
